Message: Hi babe, did you make it home okay last night? I was worried about you.
Yeah, I got home safe. Thanks for sticking around until my mum showed up. It meant a lot.
It's no problem at all :) What plans do you have this weekend?
I’ve got to look after my little brother since my mum is working. What about you? Anything exciting?
Not much, probably just hanging out with some mates. But hey, maybe we could meet up sometime? I'd love to see you again.
That sounds great! I’d really like that.
Awesome, I’ll message you soon to set something up. It was really nice meeting you last night, by the way :)
Good morning, sleepy babe. How are you feeling today?
I'm good, thanks. How about you?
I’m good too. I couldn’t stop thinking about you last night. Do you want to meet up on Wednesday?
I’d love to :) What time are you thinking?
What time do you get out of school?
How about I meet you at the park at 4pm?
Sounds great.
I’m really looking forward to it. Can’t wait to see you.
Hey Lottie, need some company tonight? ;)
Are you suggesting something?
Can I come over? I’d love to hang out with you.
I’d like that, but my mum wouldn’t be happy since I’m babysitting. How are you otherwise?
I’m doing pretty well, just been thinking about you. What about you?
I’m good, just a bit bored. Babysitting isn’t exactly thrilling.
I’m really looking forward to seeing you on Wednesday.
Me too :)
Will you be wearing that outfit you had on at the disco?
LOL no, I’ll be in my school uniform, unfortunately. :/
Even better! ;) I’m into that.
My mum’s back, I’ve got to go. See you on Wednesday :)
Bye, babe. I really can’t wait to see you again.
I had such a good time this afternoon. I wish we could’ve spent more time together.
Me too. I’m sorry I had to leave early, but my mum doesn’t like me staying out late.
I totally understand, but I just wish I could be with you all the time.
That’s really sweet of you.
Well, I think you’re really sweet too. So, when can we meet up again?
I’m not sure. Maybe we can hang out over the weekend?
How about Saturday? I really wanted to kiss you today, but I wasn’t sure if you wanted me to.
blushing
So, can we make Saturday a date for that kiss? I can’t stop thinking about it.
Yes. I’d like that.
Great :) I can’t wait! xxx
Hi Lottie, how are you? I can’t stop thinking about you. You’re absolutely amazing.
I’m really good. I keep thinking about you too.
What kind of things are you thinking about? I keep imagining how pretty you are.
I’m blushing! Do you really think that?
Of course. You’re beautiful, Lottie. I love your hair. It’s absolutely gorgeous.
Nobody’s ever said that to me before. Well, apart from my mum! LOL
Well, I’m just being honest.
Thanks. I think you’re great too.
That makes me really happy to hear.
smiles
I’m really looking forward to seeing you tomorrow.
Me too!
What do you want to do?
I don’t mind really, you choose :)
How about we grab something to eat together? Maybe get a bit of privacy.
That sounds perfect.
I had such a great time yesterday. I just wish I could see more of you.
I had a lot of fun too. How about we meet up again next week?
That’s not quite what I meant ;)
What do you mean then?
I meant that I wish I could see more of your body, if you know what I mean... ;)
blushes "Oh
So, what do you say? Will you take some special pictures of yourself for me?
Hmm, I’m not sure. I’d feel embarrassed. What if someone else saw them?
There’s nothing to be embarrassed about. You’re beautiful. I just really want to see what’s under that uniform. I promise, I’ll keep them just between us.
I don’t know...
Please? For me?
I don’t think I’m ready for that yet.
Okay, I understand. But just know that I really want you. I can’t stop thinking about it.
I’m sorry, Jack. I like you a lot, but I’m just not ready for that kind of thing.
It’s okay, babe. I’ll wait until you’re ready. Just know that I’m thinking of you.
Hi Lottie, are you free this weekend? I’ve been missing you.
Maybe on Saturday? I’ve got homework to catch up on.
Saturday works for me. I can help you with that homework if you’d like ;)
LOL thanks, but I think I’ll manage. What do you want to do?
I just want to be with you. Maybe we could go somewhere quiet, just the two of us.
I’d like that.
Only a few more days until Saturday! I’m really looking forward to it. Can’t wait to see you.
Me too. I’ve been thinking about you a lot.
Have you? What have you been thinking about?
Just about our last date. It was really nice.
I’ve been thinking about that kiss too. It was amazing. Can we do it again on Saturday? Maybe even a bit more?
I don’t know... I mean, I really like you, but I don’t want to rush things.
I understand. We’ll just take it slow. I just really like being with you.
I like being with you too.
Great :) I’ll see you on Saturday then.
